  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM10.10.7">
<l>kāmaṟ keṉkaṭavēṉ</l>
<l>karumāmukil vaṇṇaṟkallāl</l>
<l>pūmē laiṅkaṇai kōttu<supplied>p</supplied>pu kunteyyak</l>
<l>kāmaṟ keṉkaṭavēṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>What should I do against Kāma?</l>
<l>When, commencing nocking [his] five arrows with flowers, he shoots,</l>
<l>Besides [what I do] against the one like a dark cloud</l>
<l>What should I do against Kāma?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
